<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink82-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">maṉaivayiṟ pukunta pāṇaṟkut talaimakaṉ kēṭkumāṟṟāl talaimakaḷ colliyatu.
      </p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink82">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>vekuṇṭaṉa ḷeṉpa pāṇaniṉ ṟalaimakaṇ</l>
<l>makiḻnaṉ mārpi ṉaviḻiṇar naṟuntārt</l>
<l>tātuṇ paṟavai vantem</l>
<l>pōtār kūnta liruntaṉa veṉavē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

<l>   O bard! </l> 
<l> They say your mistress was furious </l> 
<l> [when she heard] that the bees that suck pollen </l> 
<l> from the fragrant garland with its opening clusters </l> 
<l> on the chest of the delightful man, </l> 
<l> came and sat on our hair,</l> 
<l> full of buds. </l> 

  
  
        </lg>
    </div>
